    <h1><i>Nutrition</i></h1>
    <p class="text1"><i>What is nutrition?</i></p>
        Well, nutrition is the process in which living things obtain nutrients and make
        use of them<br>
        There are six types of nutrients namely;<br>
                Water<br>
                vitamins<br>
                Minerals<br>
                Fats and lipids<br>
                Carbohydrates<br>
    To ensure that we get the necesaary nutrients we should eat foods consisting of all 
    nutrients in their right amounts<br>
